Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========Pre=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========OP=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.53,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:14.17,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}僕らの願いが届くまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.06,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}大事なものまた一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.68,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}モノクロの空へと消える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:34.47,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隠したキズ冷たく震え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.85,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分の居場所を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:46.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}常識に従うこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:51.38,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}どうしようもできないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.58,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}壊していきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:01:03.13,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}閉ざしたココロ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:10.58,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:16.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分さえも見失いそうになって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.15,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}曖昧な答えはイラナイ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:26.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}確かな今　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲伤的连锁之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:14.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在我们的愿望实现之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}又一件珍贵的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}消失在黑白的空中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:34.47,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隐藏的伤痕在发冷颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去找寻我的容身之处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:46.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在这个遵循常识的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:51.38,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想打破无可救药的桎梏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}按自己的意志自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:01:03.13,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}封闭的心灵正发出呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:10.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲伤的连锁之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:16.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我们几乎快要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.15,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不需要暧昧的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:26.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只需去追寻真切的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======TEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时刻不能放松戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军准备出动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从范乌哲失陷后战况不容乐观
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷戈尔将军如此不堪一击…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但考虑到对手是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非完全无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金·巩特尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战线正压向我方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更糟糕的是 失去范乌哲后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经失去了打持久战的资本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候也该有大动作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着你提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下场战役的部署即将完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必杞人忧天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候不容你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在待命便是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么对我也保密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…耶格尔将军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问件事可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么问这个…你莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们的关系远比看上去复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛尔贝莉亚 我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也是这种蓝色玫瑰的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您让我找到了自己的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有这样一起赏花了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人回想起过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站在这缕阳光下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能伴随殿下身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都源自于您的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从那时 您为我斩断枷锁以来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未来 只为您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一个个六神无主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鲁高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确认没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的话可以找我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 不过我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让你操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有会议 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说自己没事的人 往往都心事重重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里着火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…烤点面包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副问题堆积如山的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 别心不在焉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候害艾丽西娅受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功夺取范乌哲后 战争主动权正倒向我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国军失去资源供应保障后 势必策划短期决战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须密切关注帝国军动向 谨慎应对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:07:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巩特尔少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切忌松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鲁高 有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事的人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给个面子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是块掏心置腹的好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帐篷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 进去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所谓坦诚相见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“火箭筒中一株萝卜花”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“姑娘用笑颜将它栽培”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“心中深藏的…”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队里竟然还准备了这种设施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有建树的部队 待遇果然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给方面也好说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗 我们两个人独占
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的 洗第一缸水而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和我谈什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说的来着 人生在世不如意者十之八九
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身经百战的队长 在那方面还是新兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看都看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们进展不顺利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你们是指谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是那种…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我只要第七小队运转顺畅就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我给你讲个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次大战中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个新兵 刚入伍时连东南西北都分不清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因为想保卫国家 所以拿起枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入了义勇军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时一心就是打仗杀敌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这个一无所有的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过战场上的历练 终于也有了自己的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还有了喜欢的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鲁高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍 这位是我的好友拉鲁高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是今天开始加入义勇军的埃莉诺·帕罗特上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个从未谈过恋爱的大老爷们儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,略显笨拙的 也开始努力尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法是笨到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知该如何赢得那位姑娘的芳心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕比上战场还辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只因为今天和姑娘说过话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天姑娘主动向自己打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就乐不可支
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后嘛 就是约定俗成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也没有太为难他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦诚心意了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚想说出口时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从姑娘嘴里得知自己的好友也喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家潇洒 又有男人味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个值得依靠的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场上也好几次救过自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到为了姑娘 他们也更般配
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心当然挣扎过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是友情 还是自己的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是能够轻易说服自己的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是得出结论前 他的那位好友就战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过从结果看 他最后选择了友情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:13:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时一下子发生了太多事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位姑娘没有察觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算伤心 也没必要让大家都不幸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家明知才会这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃莉诺才没那么笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃莉诺就是那位帕罗特上尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 不许告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出去要你好看！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（没打算说出去 全都是你在自曝…）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样的人生不适合队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢 拉鲁高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 请收好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你不是要外出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 也没有麻烦你送我的必然性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能麻烦送我去集市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有必然性 这样能省力些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样…那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 请多关照 拉玛尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你用名字称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是心理作用 快开车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢今天陪我来购物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…反正闲着慌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 今天真是大采购啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是买给谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 哥哥看起来有点消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想给他做点好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懂事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是我唯一的亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能总是为别人操心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻木了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算不上什么坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果有朝一日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能对错的事说不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为那样的世界就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 整天恍恍惚惚的不像我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须搞个明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事想找你谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们最近不太搭调
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉尴尬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我也感觉不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的顶头上司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后总还要并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 让你有这种顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的不是道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想 像以前那样聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金呢 怎么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想继续这样尴尬下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为自己被维尔金讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说什么讨厌 我其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的…伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样法尔迪奥也会安心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要提法尔迪奥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他好像很担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我和维尔金的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和法尔迪奥有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥向我告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…法尔迪奥是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是问这些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在问维尔金的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是艾丽西娅和法尔迪奥的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没资格插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心甘情愿这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没做了 有点失败
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:46.11,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}悲しすぎる瞳が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:52.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}この空を映す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:22:01.17,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}掛ける言葉がわからずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:07.02,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただ　星を数えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:12.74,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独で居る世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:19.52,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}得意なはずだと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:26.03,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}振りかえる日々　あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:32.46,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}探していた　きみをひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:39.10,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}もしもいま許されるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:45.79,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}きみのことだけ想うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:53.68,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}忘れたくない悲しみならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:23:01.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただそれが　それだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:07.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}そう  ひとつの願い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:46.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}太过悲伤的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:52.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}映照出这片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:22:01.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}不知该说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:07.02,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只默默数着星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:12.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:19.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}早该习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:26.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}回首往日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:32.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我曾独自将你找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:39.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若此刻能得到允许
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:45.79,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我愿心中只思念着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:53.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若不愿忘却这悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:23:01.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}仅此而已 唯有此心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:07.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}是的 那是唯一的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======NEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全名就是伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达鲁库斯人自古没有姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我被巩特尔家收为养女后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一种不可思议的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.03,0:23:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥说 这就是一家人的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 战场女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17章 精灵节的馈赠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命的意义 在于与其抗争 而非屈服
